---
title: Japanese-Style Pork Katsu with Sesame Roasted Carrots & Jasmine Rice
description: It’s pretty tough to beat the rich flavor and crispy texture of Japanese katsu. In this riff on the dish, we coat pork chops in sour cream and panko, then shallow-fry them until crunchy and golden brown. Ginger-infused rice and sesame-studded roasted carrots make the perfect pairing, and Japanese Barbecue Sauce tops every bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6876417a249cc147aea83338-b2d6686f.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6876417a249cc147aea83338-en-US.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/japanese-style-pork-katsu-6876417a249cc147aea83338
time required: 35 minutes
